name: Standing tall
description:
"A beautiful view."
Those were his thoughts.
To feel as though the scales had finally fallen from his eyes. He could see the entire atmosphere above the clouds.
His journey had felt long but now it had been completed.
The Heavens had allowed him to enter the land of the giants and this was now his new place.
He was a fine warrior in life.
His a final protector in the afterlife. 
Now he could bring his tribe to order.
Now he could make a stand.
King Femi was only just beginning his reign.
The truth of how he arrived will be a story of legend told amongst the brave.
